## KEYWORD & SEO STRATEGY

### **TITLE STRUCTURE (90-100 characters)**

**For Infographics:**
```
[NUMBER] [PRIMARY KEYWORD from board name] [YEAR if seasonal] [MODIFIERS] [BENEFIT/HOOK]
```

**Examples:**
- "60 Valentine's Day Nails 2026 Pink Red Hearts Chrome Romantic Designs"
- "50 French Nails Designs Classic Modern Minimal Elegant Ideas"
- "75 Halloween Nails 2026 Spooky Cute Orange Black Purple Ideas"

**First 30 characters are CRITICAL** - they show in Pinterest feeds.

### **DESCRIPTION STRUCTURE (420-500 characters)**

**Formula:**
```
[REPEAT FIRST 4-5 WORDS OF TITLE EXACTLY] + [Natural keyword-rich description] + [Social proof language] + [Authenticity line]
```

**Rules:**
- First sentence MUST match title start word-for-word
- Naturally integrate 6-10 related keywords
- Include occasion/event context
- Add social validation: "trending", "most popular", "tried and tested"
- End with randomly selected authenticity line (see list below)
- Write in complete sentences, no keyword stuffing
- Never use hashtags in descriptions

**Example Description:**
"60 Valentine's Day Nails 2026 collection features romantic pink and red designs perfect for your date night celebration. Explore trending heart nail art, chrome metallic finishes, glitter ombre accents, and elegant French tips with love motifs. These hand-curated designs include simple ideas for short nails and elaborate styles for long nails. From cute polka dots to sophisticated burgundy wine shades, discover nail inspiration for every Valentine's moment. Hand-Curated Collection - Real Salon Designs."

